 select

 c.[CountryId],
 c.[Country]

 create view vTerritory
 AS
 select 
 t.[TerritoryId],
 c.[CountryId],
 t.[Country],
 t.[Group],
 t.[Region] 
 from [adworkstarget].[dbo].[Country] as c
 inner join [adworkstarget].[dbo].[Territory] as t
 on c.IsoCountryName = t.Country
